  "text": "Added comprehensive agent configuration tracking to the sprite generator. Now outputs a CSV file alongside the SVG that details every agent's properties: position (grid and pixel coords), body shape, eye/mouth indices, excited state, colors, and whether feet match body. This makes the sprite sheet much more useful by allowing users to find specific agents, analyze feature distributions, and reference agents by ID. The table tracks all 1500 agents with complete configuration data.",
